revised_title: Parish of Holy-Cross in Salop: Decade of Years from 1760 to 1770
tldr: This article presents a decade of vital statistics from the Parish of Holy-Cross in Salop, including baptisms, burials, and causes of death from 1760 to 1770. The data provides insights into the demographics, public health, and living conditions of the time.
scientific_discipline: Social Sciences, Art, and Humanities > Demography
